name: Luis Quiles style (Gunsmithcat)
description:
This is a style of the Spanish artist Luis Quiles aka Gunsmithcat. His works are satire, on acute social and topical topics, with a recognizable style. LORA was trained on Anything-v3.1 model (with vae from SD).

The recommended weight is 0.7-1.0.

Trigger word: gunsmithcat

My optimal settings:

CFG: 5-7

Steps: 20-25

Clip skip: 2

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras

LORA weight: 0.7-1.0

Use Hires.fix for better results!

And have fun! Kva!
